snippet.title: Airborne Empire - Official Announcement Trailer | Future of Play Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Check out the announcement trailer for Airborne Empire to learn about this upcoming sequel to Airborne Kingdom. In Airborne Empire, build, defend, and explore the skies. Craft and manage your own unique flying city among the clouds, while defeating sky pirates through smart tactics and key upgrades, and uncover hidden wonders in the expansive open world below. Unite the peoples of the world, and reforge the Airborne Empire when the game arrives on PC in 2024.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
